These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, watermelon, mango, lime
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, mouse, hamster
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard, roller, airplane
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the dog##1
3. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the horse is between the person driving the roller and the person eating watermelon##2
6. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | mango | lime  | watermelon | pumpkin  |
| Pet         | hamster    | horse  | dog       | mouse     |
| Transport   | roller     | quad-bike | airplane       | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, gardening, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, drama, romance, animation
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, volleyball, soccer, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person watching animation movies and the person who's hobby is writing##2
5. the person watching animation movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | board-games | filmmaking    | writing  | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | satire  | drama   | romance    |
| Sport         | volleyball | cycling | cricket | soccer      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, water, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, video-games, magic-tricks, camping
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, ambient, r&b, disco
1. the fan of ambient is between the fan of disco and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk         | soy-milk   | water    |
| Hobby         | video-games | camping | puzzles | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | ambient        | disco      | funk   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, egyptian, italian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, surfing, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, motorbike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the snowmobile and the japanese##2
3. the italian is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the italian is on the right of the american##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person driving the trike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | japanese        | egyptian   | american | italian |
| Sport         | surfing | climbing | skiing    | volleyball |
| Transport     | motorbike       | jet-ski     | snowmobile       | trike    |

