.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, video-games, board-games, collecting
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, badminton, tennis, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk | hot-chocolate      | mirinda       | iced-tea   |
| Hobby      | writing   | video-games  | collecting | board-games     |
| Sport      | badminton     | skateboarding | tennis        | rowing |

