.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, potato, apple, papaya
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, cooking, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, cricket, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person eating potato##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's sport is cricket##2
6. the person eating potato is between the person eating eggplant and the person eating apple##2
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | apple | potato  | eggplant | papaya      |
| Hobby   | cooking  | video-games  | card-games | filmmaking |
| Sport   | weightlifting | volleyball | golf | cricket     |

