.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, kale, nectarine, avocado
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, western, superhero, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person eating kale is between the person watching western movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
7. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | nectarine  | kale    | avocado | grapes  |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | action       | western        | martial-arts    |
| Sport         | golf | biathlon | swimming  | ice-hockey |

