.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, photography, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, romance, epic, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, guinea-pig, pony
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person watching romance movies is between the owner of the pony and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | traveling | photography | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | time-travel | romance   | epic         |
| Pet           | mouse | guinea-pig  | hedgehog   | pony      |

