2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating apricot##1
3. the fan of disco is on the left of the person eating pear##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person eating pear##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the fan of r&b and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | cherry  | apricot    | nectarine | pear       |
| Hobby         | collecting | traveling | fishing  | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | indie      | disco  | d&b     |

