.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, papaya, plum, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, cooking, collecting
4 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, hedgehog, fish
1. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating onion##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating papaya##1
3. the owner of the snake is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the owner of the snake and the person eating cauliflower##2
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is the owner of the fish##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | cauliflower  | plum | onion | papaya     |
| Hobby   | drawing | cooking   | collecting  | hiking    |
| Pet     | lizard        | fish       | snake      | hedgehog |

