The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, baking, singing, hiking
4 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish, hamster, rabbit
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is baking##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | coffee | soy-milk     | cola | tea       |
| Hobby      | singing  | hiking | camping  | baking |
| Pet        | rabbit  | goldfish      | hamster        | frog      |

