1. the person watching western movies is the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the train is the musician##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the teacher##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is between the person watching documentary movies and the musician##2
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bike is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
