.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, board-games, cooking
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, designer, freelancer, engineer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, weightlifting, badminton, rowing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the engineer##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the firefighter and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
6. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | board-games   | rock-climbing           | filmmaking         | cooking      |
| Job     | firefighter | freelancer | engineer | designer |
| Sport   | badminton     | weightlifting         | volleyball       | rowing        |

