.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, hip-hop, trance, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indonesian, nigerian
1. the fan of indie is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking coffee and the dutch##2
3. the person drinking coffee is the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the person drinking coffee is between the fan of trance and the nigerian##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the chinese is between the indonesian and the fan of punk##2
7. the fan of indie is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | coffee | juice   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | hip-hop    | trance   | punk     |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | indonesian | chinese | dutch   |

