.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, almond-milk, milk
There 4 different types of food: peas, garlic, zucchini, raspberry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, water-polo, climbing
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
2. the person eating zucchini is between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | 7up | milk           | almond-milk |
| Food       | peas | zucchini    | garlic          | raspberry   |
| Sport      | water-polo  | sailing   | climbing | parkour  |

