.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, family, superhero, scientific
4 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, frog, goldfish
1. the person watching superhero movies is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching animation movies##2
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking coffee and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | juice | almond-milk | coffee     | sprite   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | scientific        | superhero  | family  |
| Pet           | lizard      | goldfish         | bird | frog |

