3. the accountant is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is the engineer##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | accountant        | engineer  | doctor | teacher   |
| Sport       | biathlon | parkour | tennis    | badminton |
| Transport   | motorbike        | quad-bike     | airplane       | trike      |

