.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, lettuce, corn, grapes
4 different pets are kept: snake, goat, guinea-pig, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, subway, roller, van
1. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lime is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the person eating corn is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the van is the owner of the horse##1
6. the owner of the goat is between the person eating grapes and the person driving the roller##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes | lettuce | lime | corn |
| Pet         | snake       | goat     | guinea-pig   | horse   |
| Transport   | taxi | subway | roller | van |

 